{"tid":2074804,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"宮崎駿企劃 吉卜力首部 3DCG 長篇動畫《安雅與魔女》釋出主視覺及動畫場景圖","createTime":"2020-06-22T11:22:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T13:28:35.000Z","uid":20641,"like":4,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b8b98a35f5f6251c23438bea94be8cdca81e92ed","tid":2074804,"uid":20641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T11:22:00.000Z","msg":"《千與千尋》、《哈爾移動城堡》等等都是宮崎駿的經典作品，而日本吉卜力工作室自從2014年推出電影動畫《回憶中的瑪妮》後，多年來都沒有新的長篇動畫。不過在月初時就宣佈將有新作，更會在今年正式推出，近日還釋出了多張新劇照。<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.presslogic.com/girls.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/cf8648f1-815a-492d-81c7-4cedadfde397.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.presslogic.com%2Fgirls.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2Fcf8648f1-815a-492d-81c7-4cedadfde397.jpg&h=9f530761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本動畫大師宮崎駿旗下的吉卜力工作室於月初時宣佈，將會把《哈爾移動城堡》作者戴安娜&middot;韋恩&middot;瓊斯的另一款小說作品《安雅與魔女》(アーヤと魔女) 改編成動畫，並首次挑戰全編 3DCG 動畫。<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.presslogic.com/girls.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/xdnalen.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.presslogic.com%2Fgirls.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2Fxdnalen.jpg&h=60c2b610&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《安雅與魔女》由宮崎駿主導企劃，兒子宮崎吾朗擔任監督，預計今年冬天於 NHK 開播。原作故事講述在兒童之家被扶養長大的女孩「安雅」，某日被魔女所收養，她本來以為可以學到魔法所以很開心，但她被收養後，每日都被關在家中做苦工。感到不悅的安雅受到了魔女養的黑貓「湯瑪士」幫助，偷偷創造了可以對抗魔女的咒文。<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.presslogic.com/girls.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2drtqn3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.presslogic.com%2Fgirls.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F2drtqn3.jpg&h=bbd9211c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.presslogic.com/girls.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/rewwegm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.presslogic.com%2Fgirls.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2Frewwegm.jpg&h=e4fd6844&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n宮崎駿本人在評價這作品時也提到：「對孩子們來說，和難纏的大人打交道是一件辛苦的事。雖然安雅在故事裡有一點卑鄙，但卻非常可愛，希望這部作品可以為孩子們打氣，也能夠帶給大人們更多的能量。」宮崎駿的作總是會有深一層的反思和啟發。<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.presslogic.com/girls.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/3yv7sqd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.presslogic.com%2Fgirls.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F3yv7sqd.jpg&h=b13ee51d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.presslogic.com/girls.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/s1opc0h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.presslogic.com%2Fgirls.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2Fs1opc0h.jpg&h=c02308c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.presslogic.com/girls.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/zap84bw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.presslogic.com%2Fgirls.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2Fzap84bw.jpg&h=d70f9d98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而這次更是吉卜力工作室多年來首次捨棄手繪傳統，改為電腦繪圖的 3D 動畫，最近官方還一口氣釋出了多張劇照，整個風格都大改變！不管是人物外型、神情、或是服裝都跟以前經典的宮崎駿風格好不一樣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.presslogic.com/girls.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/ddauaao.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.presslogic.com%2Fgirls.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2Fddauaao.jpg&h=2486e94b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民更指甚至有皮克斯動畫的味道，而看慣了2D平面呈現的吉卜力風格動畫的女生，又有沒有覺得這次宮崎駿帶來的新時代好衝激呢？大家又期待《安雅與魔女》嗎？"},{"pid":"6e0323e8bc83bebd0f84c1e81f26e4f1b7c3601f","tid":2074804,"uid":84926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T11:28:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45ed4a398d1e855b62d158602acfadf9cdf224a3","tid":2074804,"uid":273289,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T11:30:47.000Z","msg":"唔知係唔係多支那後製 有蝗味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2748343f6da169a2303edeb0ac944b46b8a285de","tid":2074804,"uid":117009,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T11:31:04.000Z","msg":"睇宮崎駿都係想睇佢啲畫姐..."},{"pid":"089ef631abae44ec020d0f40a272cf936fbf2f96","tid":2074804,"uid":35112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T11:38:54.000Z","msg":"cg有咩意思"},{"pid":"cfe3c80a74718a4ca637968ca7b15c59823eaf96","tid":2074804,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T11:39:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b82d9757a61f1720fec4e33309a2eedff59c5184","tid":2074804,"uid":235152,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T11:59:38.000Z","msg":"睇得多迪迪尼,望落去用色唔夠自然"},{"pid":"e14349e1146aa92ff8310c01b24b0648fccf29fb","tid":2074804,"uid":260756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45ed4a398d1e855b62d158602acfadf9cdf224a3","tid":2074804,"uid":273289,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T11:30:47.000Z","msg":"唔知係唔係多支那後製 有蝗味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T12:02:07.000Z","msg":"眼唔入眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf7d64518f05c914caecec132e2afb6c450bda0","tid":2074804,"uid":308450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T12:03:48.000Z","msg":"好pixar"},{"pid":"ece1b78309e865459d818db875958bd750244224","tid":2074804,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T12:53:24.000Z","msg":"呢個水準... 收返埋吧"},{"pid":"6c8a14a933f9a19c7a5f95aedf2e80889c0f596e","tid":2074804,"uid":25653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:53:05.000Z","msg":"韓國做果d cg卡通片就係咁嘅色同質地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5227c96d8d56fbb50deab28e52ad3817074c1b0","tid":2074804,"uid":121617,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:11:58.000Z","msg":"完全無興趣<br />\n無哂吉卜力既優點"},{"pid"