ke":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T20:51:22.000Z","msg":"似恐怖game畫面多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其個女主角 凝住佢要學魔法捉鬼"},{"pid":"080400603a5c6f56a1ab779c7f2d6cab6fc5f12f","tid":2074804,"uid":49044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:03:24.000Z","msg":"細緻度輸哂disney pixar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我明佢係啱啱起步<br />\n但至少唔使全cg呀嘛<br />\n可以係手繪加cg<br />\n日本動畫已經可以做到好好手繪cg融合<br />\n例如ufo嘅fate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nGhibli咁樣會比其他日本studio比下去<br />\n唔好講disney pixar"},{"pid":"e26aa6d4153cb65e63f3eef09320417b0f2d8a33","tid":2074804,"uid":67307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:19:01.000Z","msg":"d光打得有問題"},{"pid":"11820523c9b9f701affafa28f44e770a93f99c16","tid":2074804,"uid":35424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:21:57.000Z","msg":"泥膠?"},{"pid":"ce1f16deaca67257672174a477b72479552680a2","tid":2074804,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29f69ec7ec3f89610ffc83d3c2cc98f8d736cb57","tid":2074804,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T12:51:38.000Z","msg":"有新嘗試係好事,但係咪有必要全3D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋呢套野係宮崎吾朗整,真係好難期望"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:28:35.000Z","msg":"睇過套紀錄片 佢根本無天份"}]}